{"tid":777028,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有睇Netflix套 REA(L)OVE","createTime":"2018-08-12T14:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T06:43:07.000Z","uid":82018,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"562ed39e9560550abaade0320684da1d410b5b06","tid":777028,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/222337_2179185f905b4b9abe97467e18ec9188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F222337_2179185f905b4b9abe97467e18ec9188.jpg&h=3746242d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=To3iuNEOsKY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTo3iuNEOsKY&d=cjvTy4WQQsd0d8J0Y8YlPwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=5d569db7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=To3iuNEOsKY</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>簡介</strong><br />\n關於愛情，我們總是能冠冕堂皇的說著不重視條件、背景或過去，只在乎找到最適合彼此的真愛，但誠實一點的面對自己的心，卻並非如此。Netflix最近播出的日本實境節目《REA(L)OVE》，就是要讓你看見人們面對愛情時的黑暗的樣貌。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<strong>你會一直對我一樣嗎？</strong><br />\n<br />\n由曾經主持過《戀愛糾察隊 》的田村淳和前早安少女組歌手矢口真里擔任主持人，將18位男女聚集在沖繩的度假村中，進行一系列的互動。參與的每個人都表示自己是到節目尋求真愛的可能，但卻全都隱藏起自己的黑歷史，直到被抽籤點名才公開。<br />\n<br />\n參加人員的黑歷史有包含濫交、性別認同障礙、曾經犯罪，又或是背負巨額債務，以及有特殊癖好和職業等等，讓參加的男女在未知的情況下，去了解彼此個性而產生好感，直到公佈黑歷史之後，再讓彼此重新定義或考慮是否要繼續深交。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://www.adaymag.com/2018/05/07/netflix-realove.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaymag.com%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2Fnetflix-realove.html&d=cjvTy4WQQsd0d8J0Y8YlPwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=b41ca6d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.adaymag.com/2018/05/07/netflix-realove.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人想一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一開始已經會對參賽者有一定嘅睇法，<br />\n但聽到佢地嘅故事／佢地嘅行為又會改觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係又吉，一開始覺得佢好克人憎，但聽到佢嘅原因即刻理解左佢嘅諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「秘密也只是一個人的其中一面，只是一部份而已。」"},{"pid":"9ff6a2f1f58139f1652218a6a6890ab208fb670b","tid":777028,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"無人睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"16d63ccce780a3a32a2b6312360c9e3d8358c3a0","tid":777028,"uid":34698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea31063fc00fe11c27a04cd35bd250aebd115579","tid":777028,"uid":92433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T06:43:07.000Z","msg":"睇左,好多av人又性上癮又濫交既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}